and-facebook-partner-on-new-app-based-shopping-feature ) :

Two of tech=E2=80=99s largest players, Amazon.com Inc. and Facebook parent =
Meta Platforms Inc., are testing a feature that lets shoppers buy Amazon pr=
oducts directly from ads on Instagram and Facebook. The initiative, which i=
nvolves asking consumers to link their Amazon accounts to their social-medi=
a profiles, could make Meta more attractive to advertisers and let Amazon a=
ttract more shoppers from outside its web store.

