sable market for its logistics service, just as AWS long ago dramatically i=
ncreased the total addressable market for Amazon=E2=80=99s back-end infrast=
ructure, once again giving Amazon even better leverage on its unmatched wil=
lingness to invest.

The parameters of that deal =E2=80=94 particularly the fact that Amazon see=
med much more motivated to make it happen than Shopify =E2=80=94 helped key=
 me in on the point I made above about how merchants want their business ce=
ntered on Shopify. The fact Amazon was so eager to make it work, though, sp=
eaks to Amazon=E2=80=99s priorities: volume, first and foremost.

I suspect this also explains this deal: Amazon is ok =E2=80=94 eager, in fa=
ct =E2=80=94 for transactions to happen away from Amazon.com, and that incl=
udes transactions on Meta=E2=80=99s platform. The challenge in making this =
deal, though, are the same challenges that were at play with Shopify: Amazo=
n is providing a guarantee not to merchants but to customers about the qual=
ity of delivery, ease of return, etc., and that means knowing something abo=
ut the customer and the transaction. That, I think, explains why this partn=
ership will require customers to, at some point, link their Amazon and Meta=
 accounts: this will be a barrier at the beginning, but a link only needs t=
o happen once, at which point Meta will be able to perfectly track the tran=
saction even as Amazon gets the data it needs to execute on its logistics p=
romise.

The pay-off is, once gain, a win-win: Meta gets better tracking, and thus b=
etter performing ads, while Amazon gets more volume, both as a first order =
concern in terms of Meta ads, but also as a second order in that letting Me=
ta have the key data will drive even more conversions in the long run. Reme=
mber that for all of Amazon ads=E2=80=99 outsized success they are still ab=
out skimming money from intent-based search: Meta excels at finding people =
at the top-of-the-funnel, and introducing them to products they didn=E2=80=
=99t even know they wanted.

